Astaga, kebetulan sekali!

153
00:10:57,504 --> 00:11:02,051
Lihat, siapa yang datang!
Allie, ingat Noah, 'kan?

154
00:11:02,217 --> 00:11:03,594
- Ya, aku ingat.
- Sungguh?

155
00:11:03,719 --> 00:11:05,137
- Kemarilah.
- Fin.

156
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:06,430
- Hai.
- Hai.

157
00:11:06,889 --> 00:11:08,724
- Senang bertemu denganmu lagi.
- Sama-sama.

158
00:11:09,183 --> 00:11:11,185
- Kau tampak cantik.
- Terima kasih.

159
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:14,897
- Amat cantik.
- Kau memang cantik. Kau juga tampan.

160
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:18,067
Aku juga sangat tampan, jadi,
mari kita menonton filmnya, ya?

161
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:21,403
- Filmnya sudah mau diputar.
- Silakan.

162
00:11:21,904 --> 00:11:23,697
Kau kembali, Li'l Abner.

163
00:11:23,781 --> 00:11:26,158
Kau tak akan bisa
menangkapku, Daisy Mae!

164
00:11:26,241 --> 00:11:28,744
Ini harinya Sadie Hawkins,
aku seharusnya menangkapmu!

165
00:11:28,911 --> 00:11:30,370
Aku lebih cepat darimu.

166
00:11:30,496 --> 00:11:31,914
Naiklah kemari!

167
00:11:32,331 --> 00:11:34,208
Tidak!

168
00:11:34,374 --> 00:11:36,168
Aku akan menangkapmu!

